00:39:27,996 --> 00:39:30,610
I would never invade
your privacy like that.

489
00:39:30,646 --> 00:39:32,312
But you already have.

490
00:39:34,676 --> 00:39:35,503
Lex...

491
00:39:37,207 --> 00:39:39,341
